main.user_prompt_template:
Given a {category} dataset, map the following input columns to the standard columns.
Input columns: {input_columns}

Standard columns:
Mandatory: {mandatory_columns}
Optional: {optional_columns}

Provide the mapping in JSON format where keys are standard columns and values are matched input columns. Map only when confident, otherwise use null as the value. Prioritize mapping mandatory columns. Response should be valid JSON.
